entry.title: Indian Army TES 50 Course Notification 2023 Apply 90 Vacancy
entry.summary: Indian Army has Released a Notification for TES-50 Course. Candidates who are interested may send Online applications for the 10+2 Technical Entry Scheme (TES-50) for Permanent Commission. The last date to apply is 30th June 2023. Interested candidates can apply at joinindianarmy.nic.in.
